<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
{% render '_doc-head.liquid' %}
<body>
{% render '_page-head.liquid' %}
<div id="page">
  <div id="help">
    <main>
{% unless distributable %}      <h1>Online Help</h1>
{% else %}      <h1>User Manual</h1>{% endunless %}
      <h2>Edit Favourites</h2>
      <p>Edit favourite channels, channel reference, stream type.</p>
      <p>Reference properties and stream properties.</p>
      <div id="howto" class="l1">
        <h3>How to edit</h3>
        <p>Select the favourite channel to edit, open the context menu and click on <b>&quot;Edit Favourite&quot;</b>.</p>
        <p>In <b>dialog</b>, edit the favourite parameters, then press <b>&quot;Save&quot;</b>.</p>
        <div class="l2">
          <p>Favourite can be quickly edited by <b>double-click</b>ing on selected favourite channel.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div id="reference" class="l1">
        <h3>Properties <span class="type">[Reference]</span></h3>
        <p>From <b>Reference</b> group you will change the following reference properties:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>Favourite type</b>, favourite type, eg. 1 [broadcast], 2 [file], 4097 [custom], &hellip;</li>
          <li><b>Entry flag</b>, favourite bit-flag, eg. 0 [null], 64 [marker], &hellip;</li>
          <li><b>Service type</b>, service type, eg. 0 [Data], 1 [TV], 2 [Radio], &hellip;</li>
          <li><b>Service ID</b>, service identifier</li>
          <li><b>Transport ID</b>, Transport Stream identifier</li>
          <li><b>DVBNS</b>, DVB namespace identifier from Enigma 2 specs</li>
          <li><b>ONID</b>, network identifier</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div id="stream" class="l1">
        <h3>Properties <span class="type">[Stream]</span></h3>
        <p>From <b>Stream</b> group you will change the following stream properties:</p>
        <ul>
          <li><b>Channel URL</b>, URL of the reference channel</li>
          <li><b>Channel name</b>, name of the reference channel</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div id="channel" class="l1">
        <h3>Edit from channel <span class="type">[Bouquet only]</span></h3>
        <p>Select the service channel to edit, open the context menu and click on <b>&quot;Edit Service&quot;</b>.</p>
        <p>To change the favourite parameters, go to <b>Favourite</b> tab.</p>
        <p>Edit the favourite parameters, then return to <b>Service</b> tab or press <b>&quot;Save&quot;</b>.</p>
        <div class="l2">
          <p>Note: <i>The <b>Favourite</b> tab will be shown only when edit from user bouquets.</i></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="ls">
        <p>For channel lists guide follow <a href="channel-lists.html">Channel List operations</a> page of online help.</p>
        <p>For transponders guide follow <a href="transponders.html">Transponder operations</a> page of online help.</p>
      </div>
{% render '_page-dist.liquid', help_rev: help_rev %}
    </main>
{% render '_page-side.liquid' %}
  </div>{% unless distributable %}
{% render '_page-foot.liquid' %}{% endunless %}
</div>
{% render '_page-vars.liquid' %}
</body>
</html>
